to get them to $4 an hour, the cost is $20,000. Right, exactly. Right, exactly. It's $20,000. It's nothing. It's nothing. In a budget of $217 million, it's nothing. That's stupid. This is the theme of the evening. I can't say it enough times. You're not saving anything.

